page.title: 19Economics
page.content: This is not a{poor}area in fact far from it. One is either from a long line of{Aristocrats}living in the local Manor house,or from a long line of well-known{farmers}to which the farm has been handed down from {generation}to generation. If one is not from the above catergory then one falls into the{middle}or {lower}class catergory where you will find that both parents are working to provide the{needs}of their families. Despite the current{economic climate the children in this area do not appear lacking in any{material wants.
